'''Fire ship''' can refer to:
*The [[F-143 emergency speeder|fireship]] in [[canon]];
*The [[Emergency firespeeder/Legends|emergency firespeeder]] in [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]];
*Any ship used to ram enemy craft or installations in order to damage them (eg. the [[GR-75 medium transport/Legends|GR-75 medium transport]] during the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]).
{{Disambig}}
